# ğŸ“ SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
#
# 1. Razorpay Setup:
#    - Sign up at https://razorpay.com/
#    - Go to Settings > API Keys
#    - Generate Test/Live keys
#    - Copy Key ID and Key Secret
#    - For webhooks: Settings > Webhooks > Add webhook URL
#    - Webhook URL: http://your-domain.com/api/payments/webhook/razorpay
#    - Events to subscribe: payment.authorized, payment.captured, payment.failed
#
# 2. Stripe Setup:
#    - Sign up at https://stripe.com/
#    - Go to Developers > API keys
#    - Copy Publishable key and Secret key
#    - For webhooks: Developers > Webhooks > Add endpoint
#    - Endpoint URL: http://your-domain.com/api/payments/webhook/stripe
#    - Events to subscribe: checkout.session.completed, payment_intent.succeeded, payment_intent.payment_failed, charge.refunded
#
# 3. Testing:
#    - Use test keys for development
#    - Test card numbers:
#      * Razorpay: 4111 1111 1111 1111 (CVV: any, Expiry: future date)
#      * Stripe: 4242 4242 4242 4242 (CVV: any 3 digits, Expiry: future date)
#
# 4. Production:
#    - Replace test keys with live keys
#    - Update APP_URL to production domain
#    - Configure webhook URLs with production domain
#    - Enable webhook signature verification
#
